title: Bangkok City Thai Restaurant
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Offers over 20 vegetarian starters and main courses, of which some are vegan. Member of the Dutch Vegetarian Association and has the vegan-friendly sticker from the Dutch Vegan Society; members of either organization receive a 10% discount. Gluten-free or salt-less items are possible. Offers cooking workshops (inquire about vegetarian/vegan).
